{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Bgy74XGuVegTWEABLEacP1","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile the final report.\n\n## Profile Page Structure Report\n\nI've thoroughly explored the frontend profile and settings components. Here's the complete breakdown:\n\n### 1. Route Definition\n- **Path**: `/profile`\n- **Route Component**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx` (line 379)\n- **Error Boundary**: Wrapped in `<RouteErrorBoundary label=\"Profile\">` to prevent crashes in other sections\n\n### 2. Profile Page Structure\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx`\n\n**Layout Overview:**\n- **Header Section**:\n  - Avatar (clickable, opens AvatarSelectorModal)\n  - Username with inline edit capability (pencil icon toggle)\n  - Level progress bar\n  - RNG Buff indicator (Heater buff countdown timer)\n  \n- **Tab Navigation** (3 tabs):\n  - `stats` → Statistics tab\n  - `transactions` → Transactions tab\n  - `settings` → Settings tab\n\n- **Content Area**: Dynamic based on active tab\n\n### 3. Settings Tab Component\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileSettings.tsx`\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Connected Wallet**\n   - Displays truncated + full wallet address\n   - Read-only display\n\n2. **Connected Socials**\n   - Discord: connect/disconnect buttons, shows username when connected\n   - X (Twitter): connect/disconnect buttons, shows handle when connected\n   - Mock OAuth flows (simulated with 500ms delays in context)\n\n### 4. Other Profile Sections\n\n- **ProfileStats.tsx** (Statistics tab)\n  - Aggregate stats: Games Played, Total Wagered, Total Wins, Net Profit, Win Rate, Best Streak\n  - Per-game breakdown table (Coinflip, Jackpot, Crypto Crash, Close Call, Game of Trades)\n\n- **ProfileTransactions.tsx** (Transactions tab)\n  - Real API data from backend via `useTransactions()` hook\n  - Paginated table with columns: Time, Game, Type, Amount, Explorer Link\n  - Cursor-based pagination\n  - SOL/USD price display (via `useSolPrice()` hook)\n  - Deep-links to individual match pages\n\n- **ProfileLoot.tsx** (not in tabs but available)\n  - Loot claiming system\n\n### 5. Context & Hooks\n\n**Main Context**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/context/PlayerProfileContext.tsx`\n\n**Key Methods in `usePlayerProfile()`:**\n- `myProfile`: Current user's profile (null if not connected)\n- `updateUsername(username)`: Simulate 300ms network delay\n- `updateAvatar(avatarId)`: Change avatar\n- `connectDiscord()`: Mock OAuth (500ms delay, generates fake username)\n- `disconnectDiscord()`: Remove Discord connection\n- `connectTwitter()`: Mock OAuth (500ms delay, generates fake handle)\n- `disconnectTwitter()`: Remove Twitter connection\n- `getProfile(address)`: Lookup any player's profile\n- `loadProfile(address)`: Async profile fetch (100ms simulated)\n- `claimLoot(lootId)`, `claimAllLoot()`: Loot claiming\n\n**Integration Hooks:**\n- `useWallet()` from `@rng-utopia/wallet/hooks` - gets connected address\n- `useBossRaid()` - for RNG Buff indicator\n- `useTransactions()` - fetches real transaction history from backend API\n- `useSolPrice()` - fetches SOL/USD price (refreshes every 60s)\n\n### 6. Data Types\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/types.ts`\n\n**Key Interfaces:**\n```typescript\nPlayerProfile {\n  address, username, avatarId\n  level, currentXP, totalXP\n  discordUsername, twitterHandle\n  stats: PlayerStats\n  unclaimedLoot: LootItem[]\n  createdAt, lastActiveAt\n}\n\nPlayerStats {\n  gamesPlayed, totalWagered, netProfit, wins, losses\n  currentWinStreak, bestWinStreak\n  gameStats: Record<GameId, GameSpecificStats>\n}\n\nProfileTransaction {\n  id, gameId, matchId, txType, amountLamports, txSig, createdAt\n}\n```\n\n**Constants:**\n- Username: min 3, max 20 chars, alphanumeric + underscores only\n- Games: coinflip, lord-of-rngs, crypto-crash, close-call, game-of-trades\n- Avatars: 13 tiers from \"Recruit\" (Lv1) to \"Cosmic Deity\" (Lv100)\n- Avatar tier colors defined for UI display\n\n### 7. Backend Integration\n\n**Transaction API**: `GET /profile/transactions?limit=20&cursor=X&game=Y`\n- Requires JWT Bearer token from `getAccessToken()`\n- Cursor-based pagination\n- Response: `{transactions[], nextCursor}`\n\n**Price API**: `GET /price/sol-usd`\n- Public endpoint\n- Response: `{price: number}`\n\n### File Paths Summary\n\n```\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/\n├── components/\n│   ├── ProfilePage.tsx (main page, tab navigation)\n│   ├── ProfileSettings.tsx (wallet + socials)\n│   ├── ProfileStats.tsx (statistics)\n│   ├── ProfileTransactions.tsx (transaction history)\n│   ├── ProfileLoot.tsx (loot claiming)\n│   ├── PlayerAvatar.tsx\n│   ├── PlayerAvatarCompact.tsx\n│   ├── AvatarSelectorModal.tsx\n│   └── others\n├── context/\n│   └── PlayerProfileContext.tsx (provider + usePlayerProfile hook)\n├── hooks/\n│   ├── useTransactions.ts\n│   └── useSolPrice.ts\n├── types.ts (all type definitions)\n├── index.ts (public API exports)\n└── utils/\n    ├── profile-event-bus.ts\n    └── mock-simulation.ts\n```"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a820d5fc4a84d6848 (use SendMessage with to: 'a820d5fc4a84d6848' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 61483\ntool_uses: 17\nduration_ms: 59843</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eb5de170-2e49-4887-a19e-0983dec4d654","uuid":"4b747367-5a24-48b8-a69a-adafdacb1a29","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:39:07.978Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find and read the profile page/settings components in the frontend. Look in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/` for 